<div class="jumbotron">
  <h1 class="display-4"><%= @school.name %></h1>
  <p class="lead">We are still in the process of setting up your school on Energy Sparks. You will get an email notification when your school's account is activated on Energy Sparks.</p>

  <p>
    In the meantine, take a look at how
    <% if @school.school_group.present? %>
      <%= link_to 'schools in your area', school_group_path(@school.school_group) %> are using Energy Sparks
    <% else %>
      <%= link_to 'other schools', schools_path %> are using Energy Sparks
    <% end %>
  </p>
</div>
